OL,3,CNHS to roll out Martha's Rule for
OL,4,Cpatients' right to urgent second
OL,5,Copinion
OL,7,FSejal Karia reports as more than 100
OL,8,Fhospitals prepare to roll out
OL,9,F'Martha's Rule', which would allow a
OL,10,Fsecond medical opinion if a patient's
OL,11,Fcondition is rapidly worsening.
OL,13,FThe NHS in England will roll out
OL,14,F'Martha's Rule' from April to give
OL,15,Fpatients and families access to a
OL,16,Frapid review if they are .
