OL,3,CNHS to roll out Martha's Rule for
OL,4,Cpatients' right to urgent second
OL,5,Copinion
OL,7,FThe escalation process, which
OL,8,Fformalises access to a critical care
OL,9,Fteam for a second opinion, will be
OL,10,Favailable 24/7 and will be advertised
OL,11,Fthroughout hospitals.
OL,13,FUnder the move, an urgent clinical
OL,14,Freview would be carried out by a
OL,15,Fdifferent team in the hospital if a
OL,16,Fpatient's condition is rapidly
OL,17,Fworsening and they or their family
OL,18,Ffeels they are not getting the care
OL,19,Fneeded.
