OL,3,CNHS to roll out Martha's Rule for
OL,4,Cpatients' right to urgent second
OL,5,Copinion
OL,7,FAt least 100 NHS trusts are expected
OL,8,Fto bring in the rule, with the
OL,9,Fprogramme evaluated throughout this
OL,10,Fyear and next.
OL,12,FThe plan is to then extend Martha's
OL,13,FRule to all acute hospitals, subject
OL,14,Fto government funding.
OL,16,FThe move follows the death of 13-year-
OL,17,Fold Martha Mills in 2021. while under
OL,18,Fthe care of King's College Hospital
OL,19,FNHS Foundation Trust in south London.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/13
