OL,3,CNHS to roll out Martha's Rule for
OL,4,Cpatients' right to urgent second
OL,5,Copinion
OL,7,FA coroner ruled she would most likely
OL,8,Fhave survived if doctors of her
OL,9,Frapidly deteriorating condition and
OL,10,Ftransferred her to intensive care
OL,11,Fearlier.
OL,13,FMartha's parents, Merope Mills, an
OL,14,Feditor at the Guardian, and her
OL,15,Fhusband Paul Laity, raised concerns
OL,16,Fabout Martha's health a number of
OL,17,Ftimes but these were brushed aside.
OL,19,FThe pair have since campaigned for
OL,20,FMartha's Rule to be introduced to give
OL,21,Ffamilies more say.
