OL,3,CNHS to roll out Martha's Rule for
OL,4,Cpatients' right to urgent second
OL,5,Copinion
OL,7,FThey said in a statement: "We are
OL,8,Fpleased that the implementation of
OL,9,FMartha's Rule will begin in April.
OL,11,F"We want it to be in place as quickly
OL,12,Fand as widely as possible, to prevent
OL,13,Fwhat happened to our daughter from
OL,14,Fhappening to other ."
OL,16,FThe pair hope the system will give
OL,17,Fpatients more power, encourage medical
OL,18,Fprofessionals to listen to those they
OL,19,Fare treating and to normalise the idea
OL,20,Fthat doctors should welcome being
OL,21,Fchallenged.
