OL,7,FShe also developed a rash and her
OL,8,Fmother voiced concerns to staff that
OL,9,FMarthaover a bank holiday weekend.
OL,11,FOne of the trust's own intensive care
OL,12,Fdoctors told the inquest into Martha's
OL,13,Fdeath he would "100%" have admitted
OL,14,Fher if he had seen her.
