OL,5,Copinion
OL,7,F"I know I speak on behalf of all when
OL,8,FI thank Merope and Paul for their
OL,9,Fextraordinary campaigning and
OL,10,Fcollaboration on this hugely important
OL,11,Fissue," she said.
OL,13,FNHS teams will also look at ways ways
OL,14,Fto roll out an adapted Martha's Rule
OL,15,Fmodel in community and mental health
OL,16,Fhospitals.
