OL,5,Copinion
OL,7,FRory Deighton, director of the NHS
OL,8,FConfederation's acute network,
OL,9,Fwelcomed the move but said there are
OL,10,Fstill questions as to how medical
OL,11,Fsettings will deliver the new scheme.
OL,13,F"Introducing a 24/7 clinical review
OL,14,Fprocess will have implementation costs
OL,15,Fand leaders will be concerned if they
OL,16,Fare just being expected to provide the
OL,17,Fadditional service without any extra
OL,18,Fresources," he said.
