OL,10,Fclinicians, patients and their
OL,11,Ffamilies."
OL,13,FHealth Secretary Victoria Atkins paid
OL,14,Ftribute to Martha's parents and
OL,15,Fdescribed the new rule as a "major
OL,16,Fboost" to patient safety".
